(493, 3, '2012-06-30 09:38:19', '2012-06-30 09:38:19', '<br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162245.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162245.jpg" alt="20120630-162245.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162309.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162309.jpg" alt="20120630-162309.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162344.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162344.jpg" alt="20120630-162344.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162257.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162257.jpg" alt="20120630-162257.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162551.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162551.jpg" alt="20120630-162551.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162612.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162612.jpg" alt="20120630-162612.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162601.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162601.jpg" alt="20120630-162601.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162622.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162622.jpg" alt="20120630-162622.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162653.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162653.jpg" alt="20120630-162653.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162823.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162823.jpg" alt="20120630-162823.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162636.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162636.jpg" alt="20120630-162636.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162929.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162929.jpg" alt="20120630-162929.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162705.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162705.jpg" alt="20120630-162705.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162903.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162903.jpg" alt="20120630-162903.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-163002.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-163002.jpg" alt="20120630-163002.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162724.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-162724.jpg" alt="20120630-162724.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-163137.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120630-163137.jpg" alt="20120630-163137.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'Ha long: where the dragon descends into the sea', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '487-revision-3', '', '', '2012-06-30 09:38:19', '2012-06-30 09:38:19', '', 487, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=493', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2, 1, '2012-04-23 15:09:27', '2012-04-23 15:09:27', '<br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120531-193913.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120531-193913.jpg" alt="20120531-193913.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>\n\nali:  Traveling is my passion. I love the opportunity for discovery that it provides. I joke that most of the decisions I make in life are guided by the single desire to have good stories to tell over dinner. I am only half joking. After losing all I owned, I once hitchhiked from Costa Rica to Arizona. I''ve slept in the same room as a green mamba - which, upon discovery, I ate. After participating in a local ceremony for warriors in West Africa, the traditional healer assures me that I am bullet-proof. I also like warm milk with cinnamon before bed, laughing until I cry, dancing without inhibition (and better yet, in costume!), and picking scabs until they bleed.\n\n\nadam:  i love music.  listening and making. especially with others.  i ride my bike a lot.  once i rode from london to budapest.  people were friendly and cars didn''t run over me.  i camped in parks and slept on stranger''s floors.  i came back with the knowledge of how much i''d taken ranch dressing and obesity for granted. i have a phd in physics and i am a huge fan of wikipedia and npr.', 'about us.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2012-06-21 15:48:27', '2012-06-21 15:48:27', '', 0, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com//?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 1),
(63, 3, '2012-06-01 00:39:17', '2012-06-01 00:39:17', '<br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120531-193913.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120531-193913.jpg" alt="20120531-193913.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'adam & ali', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-2', '', '', '2012-06-01 00:39:17', '2012-06-01 00:39:17', '', 2, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=63', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4, 3, '2012-05-31 20:48:10', '2012-05-31 20:48:10', 'Ali tallied our flights for the trip and came up with 14 total, the first five of which will occur between now and Sunday.  \n\nToday:  \nSTL -> ATL (3 hour layover)\nATL -> NYC (8.5 hour layover)\nNYC -> LHR (arrive tomorrow, 12 hour layover)\n\nAtlanta is a little out of the way, but we''ll be taking advantage of the extended layovers, scoping out New York neighborhoods and strolling through London parks.  Both will provide a welcome opportunity to leave our temporary airport homes.  I''m most excited about a gigantic slice of pizza in Brooklyn.  Ali''s looking forward to seeing a good friend in London and sampling market food.  We''ll post photos as they come.<br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061349.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061349.jpg" alt="20120601-061349.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'last day in saint louis', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'last-day-in-saint-louis', '', '', '2012-07-08 14:32:48', '2012-07-08 14:32:48', '', 0, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=4', 0, 'post', '', 0),
