(97, 2, '2012-06-03 06:17:27', '2012-06-03 06:17:27', 'Ali tallied our flights for the trip and came up with 14 total, the first five of which will occur between now and Sunday.\r\n\r\nToday:\r\nSTL -&gt; ATL (3 hour layover)\r\nATL -&gt; NYC (8.5 hour layover)\r\nNYC -&gt; LHR (arrive tomorrow, 12 hour layover)\r\n\r\nAtlanta is a little out of the way, but we''ll be taking advantage of the extended layovers, scoping out New York neighborhoods and strolling through London parks. Both will provide a welcome opportunity to leave our temporary airport homes. I''m most excited about a gigantic slice of pizza in Brooklyn. Ali''s looking forward to seeing a good friend in London and sampling market food. We''ll post photos as they come.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061349.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061349.jpg" alt="20120601-061349.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061414.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061414.jpg" alt="20120601-061414.jpg" /></a>', 'last day in saint louis', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-19', '', '', '2012-06-03 06:17:27', '2012-06-03 06:17:27', '', 4, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=97', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
