(605, 1, '2012-06-03 07:24:16', '2012-06-03 07:24:16', 'Ali tallied our flights for the trip and came up with 14 total, the first five of which will occur between now and Sunday.  \n\nToday:  \nSTL -> ATL (3 hour layover)\nATL -> NYC (8.5 hour layover)\nNYC -> LHR (arrive tomorrow, 12 hour layover)\n\nAtlanta is a little out of the way, but we''ll be taking advantage of the extended layovers, scoping out New York neighborhoods and strolling through London parks.  Both will provide a welcome opportunity to leave our temporary airport homes.  I''m most excited about a gigantic slice of pizza in Brooklyn.  Ali''s looking forward to seeing a good friend in London and sampling market food.  We''ll post photos as they come.<br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061349.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061349.jpg" alt="20120601-061349.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061414.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120601-061414.jpg" alt="20120601-061414.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'last day in saint louis', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-21', '', '', '2012-06-03 07:24:16', '2012-06-03 07:24:16', '', 4, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=605', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
