pg" alt="20120607-165958.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120608-214004.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120608-214004.jpg" alt="20120608-214004.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120608-214019.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120608-214019.jpg" alt="20120608-214019.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'bangkok: the cancun of southeast asia.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '216-revision-4', '', '', '2012-06-08 14:40:31', '2012-06-08 14:40:31', '', 216, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=241', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
