on and commoditization of other human beings just by being there.  just by looking. And yet, I was interested.  Clearly curiosity isn''t always morally neutral...  \n\nNext we were shuttled to a silver and goldsmith shop.  A woman walked us from station to station, showing us the process of transforming ore into beautifully crafted intricate jewelry.  Another floating workshop demonstrated traditional weaving techniques using thread made from lotus plants.  Then to a local cigar making "workshop" (read: a woman''s living room) where tobacco, brown sugar and other herbs were rolled together in a banana leaf. \n\nWe visited a large, golden pagoda.  In the center, worshipers bowed to 5 amorphous golden blobs.  Apparently, one hundred years ago (according to local lore), these golden Mr. Potato Heads were in the likeness of Buddha.  But, thousands of sheets of gold leaf, applied dutifully by both devotees and waywards looking to store up some good karma for a rainy day, have given these Buddhas some extra curves. \n\nWe also stopped at a very strange monastery where the monks are famed to have taught cats to literally jump through hoops.  And jump they did.  Finally solves the ever present question of ''what do monks do all day?''\n<br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231130.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231130.jpg" alt="20120619-231130.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'Inle lake', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '289-revision-5', '', '', '2012-06-19 15:18:58', '2012-06-19 15:18:58', '', 289, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=328', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(329, 3, '2012-06-19 15:22:04', '2012-06-19 15:22:04', '<br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231923.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231923.jpg" alt="20120619-231923.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231929.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231929.jpg" alt="20120619-231929.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231938.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231938.jpg" alt="20120619-231938.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231946.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231946.jpg" alt="20120619-231946.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231954.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-231954.jpg" alt="20120619-231954.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-232004.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-232004.jpg" alt="20120619-232004.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-232015.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-232015.jpg" alt="20120619-232015.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-232030.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120619-232030.j