pg" alt="20120623-135229.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120623-135301.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120623-135301.jpg" alt="20120623-135301.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'avoiding the bends in borneo', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '384-revision-2', '', '', '2012-06-23 05:53:38', '2012-06-23 05:53:38', '', 384, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=394', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
