ploads/2012/07/20120729-185027.jpg" alt="20120729-185027.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a><br /><br /><a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20120729-185332.jpg"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20120729-185332.jpg" alt="20120729-185332.jpg" class="alignnone size-full" /></a>', 'Western Rajasthan: some like it hot', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '766-revision-8', '', '', '2012-07-29 13:23:56', '2012-07-29 13:23:56', '', 766, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=786', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
