(920, 2, '2012-08-20 00:29:00', '2012-08-20 00:29:00', 'Click on the Album cover photo to view more photos from that post.\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=882"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/20120819-194058.jpg" alt="22 flights, 10 countries, and 11 weeks later" class="alignnone size-full" />22 flights, 10 countries, and 11 weeks later</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=821"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/20120807-174208.jpg" alt="Ladakh: It’s All Downhill From Here" class="alignnone size-full" />Ladakh: It’s All Downhill From Here</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=766"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20120729-172453.jpg" alt="Western Rajasthan: some like it hot" class="alignnone size-full" />Western Rajasthan: some like it hot</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=717"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20120721-171306.jpg" alt="all the south india you can fit into 5 days. and more." class="alignnone size-full" />all the south india you can fit into 5 days. and more.</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=664"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20120714-154107.jpg" alt="Adam and Ali are “It’s Complicated” with India" class="alignnone size-full" />Adam and Ali are “It’s Complicated” with India</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=607"><img src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20120709-204123.jpg" alt="motorbike blog posts" class="alignnone size-full" />Central Laos: motorbike blog posts</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=568"><img sr