ads/2012/06/20120613-132206.jpg" alt="20120603-100352.jpg" /></a>\r\n<a title="24 hours in Bagan" href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=239">24 hours In Bagan</a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=234"><img class="alignnone size-full" src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120613-121827.jpg" alt="20120603-100352.jpg" /></a>\r\n<a title="Hello Burma! Or should I call you Myanmar?…" href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=234">Hello Burma! Or should I call you Myanmar?…</a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=216"><img class="alignnone size-full" src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120607-165914.jpg" alt="20120603-100352.jpg" /></a>\r\n<a title="bangkok: the cancun of southeast asia." href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=216">bangkok: the cancun of southeast asia.</a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=153"><img class="alignnone size-full" src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120604-230051.jpg" alt="20120603-100352.jpg" /></a>\r\n<a title="india is great. horn ok please" href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=153">india is great. horn ok please</a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=102"><img class="alignnone size-full" src="http://anywherethewindblows.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20120603-091819.jpg" alt="20120603-100352.jpg" /></a>\r\n<a title="five airports, four cities, three flights, and one day later" href="http://anywherethewindblows.com/?page_id=102">five airports, four cities, three flights, one day</a>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Photo Albums', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '105-revision-31', '', '', '2012-08-20 00:29:00', '2012-08-20 00:29:00', '', 105, 'http://anywherethewindblows.com/?p=920', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
